{"tid":832422,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"家人對貓敏感，有無空氣清新機推薦？","createTime":"2018-09-22T17:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T09:58:05.000Z","uid":5398,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b18f791931713d6592a6b35f471c05705b959c","tid":832422,"uid":5398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:27:54.000Z","msg":"有無人用左邊隻牌子嘅空氣清新機之後改善到敏感(咳、打乞痴、眼痕)？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身已經成日吸塵同幫貓貓梳毛抹身，但佢真係甩好多毛同埋有啲位實在太難打掃，各位巴絲有無邊隻空氣清新機覺得好？"},{"pid":"c43a19cab10fd653e2f791e490ee65d28a115d41","tid":832422,"uid":35908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"ac5660"},{"pid":"8227a930541059f27c762c15a308462563f20496","tid":832422,"uid":126720,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T20:00:38.000Z","msg":"真心無乜意思。<br />\n除非你家人適應到個致敏源/致敏源消失。否則再勁既空氣清新機都冇用"},{"pid":"a0553bb93cd89d81af8fcaeff81fea3441bbb64e","tid":832422,"uid":2615,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T20:03:43.000Z","msg":"掉左隻貓佢"},{"pid":"1103913386353374aafd60e979c66d0e65f9a7d5","tid":832422,"uid":5398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8227a930541059f27c762c15a308462563f20496","tid":832422,"uid":126720,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T20:00:38.000Z","msg":"真心無乜意思。<br />\n除非你家人適應到個致敏源/致敏源消失。否則再勁既空氣清新機都冇用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"唔會舒緩到少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf25a81636cb228345f18882bccb980181faaab1","tid":832422,"uid":5398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c43a19cab10fd653e2f791e490ee65d28a115d41","tid":832422,"uid":35908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T17:40:04.000Z","msg":"ac5660"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"呢部有諗過，不過預計到隻貓會攤上部機當自己牀訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"